PrecisRegulations Amending the EMPLOYMENT INSURANCE REGULATIONS which redefine the term "period of employment" to make the first day worked the start of the period and the end of that period being when there is one calendar week with no work or earnings.

precis:
Regulations Amending the EMPLOYMENT INSURANCE REGULATIONS which redefine
the term "period of employment" to make the first day worked the start of
the period and the end of that period being when there is one calendar week
with no work or earnings.
